Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.93,0:23:39.18,EDC2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,100)\blur2\an1}握在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.35,0:23:42.06,EDC2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,100)\blur2}呐  和你在一起的话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.19,0:23:44.48,EDC2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,100)\blur2}不管什么困难
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.48,0:23:46.65,EDC2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,100)\blur2\an1}都不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.48,0:23:49.44,EDC2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,100)\blur2}都能安然度过  别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.24,0:23:50.32,EDC2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,100)\blur2\an1}一定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.11,0:23:56.74,EDC2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,100)\blur2}我想要用温暖的手指握住你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.79,0:24:02.50,EDC2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,100)\blur2}绝对会保护你的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.58,0:24:08.67,EDC2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,100)\blur2}约好了哟  续写那笑容的故事
