Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-----TXT-----
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.39,0:00:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(320,329)}Docking Operation
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.39,0:00:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,合体作战
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.61,0:00:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.75,0:00:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.62,0:00:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可能  不可能  不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.63,0:00:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种事太不现实了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.21,0:00:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然有怪物袭击示现引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.10,0:00:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.60,0:00:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人类？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.03,0:02:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivid Blue Operation
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.61,0:02:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一色茜  二叶葵两人  Vivid Blue合体成功
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.58,0:02:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,利用Vivid Impact将Alone击溃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.08,0:02:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同时  Blue Island全域的警戒等级从三降到一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.00,0:02:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在正进行Alone的样本回收
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.55,0:02:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吓得人一身冷汗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.22,0:02:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这东西真的是那位开发了示现引擎的一色健次郎博士吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.56,0:02:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,劳烦老师过来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.02,0:02:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是因为最近Alone的机密数据有被不法侵入的迹象
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.90,0:03:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且突破了管理局的防火墙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.24,0:03:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天手感也不错呢  小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.25,0:03:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  铃木婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.17,0:03:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.93,0:03:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弱点？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.43,0:03:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是合体的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.05,0:03:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那次幸亏我的掩护及时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.31,0:03:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那时确实很危险呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.19,0:03:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以有必要提升我们的防御力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.27,0:03:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,于是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.11,0:03:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天元理心流特训术
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.28,0:03:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光是避开可不行  要反击回去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.70,0:03:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算你这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.66,0:03:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给你这个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.33,0:03:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下来到你咯  小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.83,0:03:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.71,0:03:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二班联络总部
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.46,0:04:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有发现类似Alone碎片的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.26,0:04:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起来完全分解掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.14,0:04:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了解  终止搜查返航
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.65,0:04:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了  今天到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.94,0:04:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,屁股麻麻的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.32,0:04:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小葵振作点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.74,0:04:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能靠想  要靠感觉的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.49,0:04:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.91,0:04:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下节课是体育吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.00,0:04:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.42,0:04:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家加油
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.43,0:04:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小葵把手套摆好位置就行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.22,0:04:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会把球投进去的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.22,0:04:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.43,0:04:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.48,0:04:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一色同学  手握反了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.20,0:05:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好球
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.99,0:05:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若叶好强诶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.25,0:05:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两好球
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.13,0:05:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终于能动了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.42,0:05:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿咻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.01,0:05:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突破我防火墙的黑客的线索居然在小茜的教室里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.77,0:05:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犯人到底是何方神圣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.56,0:05:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赌上天元理心流之名
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.90,0:05:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会用三球三振将你了结
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.37,0:05:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,摄像头？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.74,0:05:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.67,0:06:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.88,0:06:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.97,0:06:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本垒打
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.56,0:06:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  向日葵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.73,0:06:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办  向日葵它…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.81,0:06:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点  小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.65,0:06:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是摄像头哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.15,0:06:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用饭粒粘不好的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.65,0:06:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  我会跟你一起去道歉的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.11,0:06:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也一起去  小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.99,0:06:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你们俩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.66,0:06:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.37,0:06:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个摄像头…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.17,0:06:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.55,0:06:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像不在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.05,0:06:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次再来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.47,0:06:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不在也没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.76,0:06:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在这里等着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.85,0:06:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为道歉还是趁早比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.89,0:06:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到了晚上肯定会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.48,0:07:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道准备一直在那里待着…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.48,0:07:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么搞的  不在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.52,0:07:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷？为什么在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.45,0:07:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向日葵？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.04,0:07:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.88,0:07:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说…是不是有点降温过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.92,0:07:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对机器来说刚好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.34,0:07:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以说才在被炉里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.47,0:07:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个…这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.55,0:07:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.31,0:07:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会用下个月打工的钱来赔的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.40,0:07:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用了  我原谅你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.48,0:07:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.40,0:07:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过相对的  让我看看你的玩偶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.99,0:07:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个…这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.58,0:07:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.83,0:08:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个…这个这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.54,0:08:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.21,0:08:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,獭君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.21,0:08:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,獭如其名？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.21,0:08:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,獭如其名呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.54,0:08:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,獭如其名啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.92,0:08:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想看看里面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.13,0:08:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个…那里的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.13,0:08:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不不不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.89,0:08:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,獭君是我很重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.81,0:08:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.15,0:08:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不需要什么朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.07,0:08:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个…这房间很有个性呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.16,0:08:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四宫同学喜欢工厂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.62,0:08:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.45,0:08:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么工厂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.04,0:08:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,整流工厂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.92,0:08:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向全世界输送示现能量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.05,0:08:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.21,0:08:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.34,0:08:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.68,0:08:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是夕阳斜照的时候最漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.97,0:09:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶  这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.85,0:09:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好想看看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.85,0:09:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呐  现在就去看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.81,0:09:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也想看看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.65,0:09:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是呢  反正就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.73,0:09:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去看吧  向日葵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.98,0:09:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在就去？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.82,0:09:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.82,0:09:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.53,0:09:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶？为什么啊  去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.20,0:09:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为好热  有虫子  又会累
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.08,0:09:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且还在外面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.92,0:09:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行吗  是最漂亮的不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.42,0:09:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我也没有衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.42,0:09:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衣服？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.88,0:09:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.56,0:09:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.27,0:09:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向日葵好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.35,0:09:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就觉得会很合适
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.14,0:09:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的眼光果然不会错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.35,0:09:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这衣服哪来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.61,0:09:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个…这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.57,0:09:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么都好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.28,0:10:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四宫同学  头发好漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.78,0:10:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.91,0:10:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了  这个我也带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.08,0:10:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  好  好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.01,0:10:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胸口这里好紧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.64,0:10:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.80,0:10:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绝景呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.26,0:10:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好看的不仅是外观
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.85,0:10:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么庞大规模的机械
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.60,0:10:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,运作起来却无人控制这点才最为壮观
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.65,0:10:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是  是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.44,0:10:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正你们也觉得我是个怪人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.90,0:10:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有那回事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.49,0:10:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我也很喜欢示现引擎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.20,0:10:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别说的那么随意
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.62,0:10:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,示现引擎有多伟大你真的清楚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.04,0:10:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你清楚它的存在对世人是多么大的恩惠吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.71,0:10:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四宫同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.51,0:11:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我所谓的喜欢就是指这些
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.05,0:11:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别把我和你混为一谈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.39,0:11:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一样的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.97,0:11:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发明与科学是用来使人幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.98,0:11:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸妈妈和爷爷都这么说了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.48,0:11:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也这么认为
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.98,0:11:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以说是一样的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.45,0:11:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然黑客就是那个女孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.49,0:11:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这可是不得了的人才啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.37,0:11:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是还比不上我就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.08,0:11:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的名字好像是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.83,0:11:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,茜  一色茜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.54,0:11:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一色…难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.43,0:11:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,避难命令？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.01,0:11:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.24,0:12:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  整流工厂…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.87,0:12:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紧急制动装置失灵  能量暴走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.75,0:12:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必须要马上去阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.00,0:12:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.84,0:12:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个要是被破坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.01,0:12:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全世界的能源供给就没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.76,0:12:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算你这么说  我们也无能为力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.39,0:12:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明我能做得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.90,0:12:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能进入整流模块区的话  多少还是有办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.99,0:12:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小葵  若叶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.95,0:12:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.53,0:12:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ignition
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.83,0:12:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Texture ON
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.89,0:13:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.93,0:13:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我把向日葵带到工厂里去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.85,0:13:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  另一边就交给我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.40,0:13:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要小心啊  小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.40,0:13:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.33,0:13:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和怪物战斗的是你们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.21,0:13:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之后一定会来接你的  约好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.59,0:13:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.85,0:13:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naked Blade
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.81,0:14:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naked Impact
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.95,0:14:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naked Rang
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.16,0:14:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.08,0:14:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小茜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.12,0:14:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.17,0:14:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个Alone  是之前干掉的那个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.54,0:14:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉好像比上次更强了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.46,0:14:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是进化了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.68,0:14:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从这里开始
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.01,0:14:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,禁止通行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.60,0:14:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了  要赶上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.32,0:14:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.13,0:15:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求你了  向日葵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.34,0:15:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望你能做点什么制止欺辱的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.97,0:15:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让留言的人的名字都显示出来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.43,0:15:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想大家就不会做这种事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.26,0:15:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,Banner;5;0;50;0,{\fad(200,200)\fs16\an8\fnstxihei\c&H00383838H\4c&H96000000H\bord0\shad1}「好难交流…」「快点转校转走吧」「无视她吗」「无视决定！」「同一个班真讨厌」「别来学校了」「太阴沉了」「把她的室内用鞋藏起来吗」「藏哪儿啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.72,0:15:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但要是被别人知道是我做的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.98,0:15:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  知道的只有我们两个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.02,0:15:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绝对会保密吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.44,0:15:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我保证
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.28,0:15:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,Banner;5;0;50;0,{\fad(200,200)\fs16\an8\fnstxihei\c&H00383838H\4c&H96000000H\bord0\shad1}「真不想让她给我们分饭」「啊~  我能懂~」「体育课的时候别粘过来」「快到一边去」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.36,0:15:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做得真过分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.41,0:15:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太过分了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.20,0:15:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.70,0:15:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太差劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.29,0:15:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是  不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.00,0:15:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…向日葵做的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.72,0:15:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明约好了会来接我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.89,0:16:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然  果然  约定什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.56,0:16:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向日葵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.07,0:16:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉来迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.75,0:16:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么  你为什么回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.88,0:16:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为约好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.97,0:16:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.47,0:16:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.68,0:16:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是向日葵的钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.15,0:16:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的…钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.36,0:16:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能做得到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.28,0:17:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也  我也能战斗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.96,0:17:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.22,0:17:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ignition
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.89,0:17:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Texture ON
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.06,0:18:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.56,0:18:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去的话  Blue Island要被…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.44,0:18:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naked Collider
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.34,0:18:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.01,0:18:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四宫同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.51,0:18:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.80,0:18:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是我们的新伙伴  不
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.39,0:18:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是朋友哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.79,0:19:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又升级了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.13,0:19:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一点一点的好恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.84,0:19:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能听到吗  茜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.30,0:19:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.55,0:19:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它体内产生了高能量反应
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.09,0:19:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不快点解决掉会很危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.43,0:19:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是要怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.18,0:19:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等  让我想想有什么方法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.31,0:19:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.19,0:19:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们能做到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.28,0:19:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Operation
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.36,0:19:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivid Yellow
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.43,0:20:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小茜和
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.31,0:20:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四宫同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.02,0:20:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然合体了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.44,0:20:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个小女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.23,0:20:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这么短的时间里就理解Vivid系统了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.12,0:20:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.16,0:20:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivid Collider
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.54,0:20:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.54,0:20:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivid引擎  安全限制解除
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.64,0:20:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivid引擎  输出120%
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.02,0:20:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,输出150%
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.65,0:20:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,200%
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.15,0:21:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs16\pos(320,332)}Final Operation
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.15,0:21:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tiro Finale
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.26,0:21:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你居然就是一色健次郎博士的孙女
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.19,0:21:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是伟大的才能似乎没有遗传到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.65,0:21:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然连摄像机都修不好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.36,0:21:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,普通人都修不好的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.90,0:21:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.99,0:21:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.78,0:21:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为已经不需要了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.04,0:21:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明天开始去学校
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.83,0:21:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向日葵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.29,0:22:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  难得帮你修好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.33,0:22:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个莫非没用了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.34,0:22:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.84,0:22:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一色博士  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.67,0:22:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错  我就是一色健次郎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.09,0:22:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个  我从很早开始就很尊敬您了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.43,0:22:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.97,0:22:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请给我签名吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.22,0:22:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦  这是我写的书吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.39,0:22:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  是我很喜欢读的书
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.35,0:22:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师所提出的相对于真空能量的示现能量的实用性…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.65,0:22:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四宫同学
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.82,0:22:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她在说什么一点也听不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.20,0:22:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向日葵看起来很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.66,0:22:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不错啊  能发现这个
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.45,0:22:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根据我的猜想…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.50,0:22:42.50,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(560,345)}待续
